Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.29,Ep_Title - Sus Maid,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2\fs18}{Episode 2:      }{\fscx73}{The Young Master, the Cat, and the Morning Glory}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:47.04,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, your clothing.}Quần áo của chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:52.20,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll be waiting with your breakfast ready.}Tôi sẽ chuẩn bị bữa ăn sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.02,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{New clothes again.}Lại quần áo mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.63,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I've gotten pretty used \Nto living with Lilith.}Mình đã quen với cuộc sống có Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:14.88,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:19.11,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Something's still suspicious about her.}Quả nhiên vẫn đáng ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.72,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Man...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.51,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's so hot.}Nóng quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's meunière today, huh?}Hôm nay ăn meunière à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:37.86,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Delicious!}Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I will answer it.}Tôi sẽ ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.54,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Who could be here so early in the morning?}Sáng sớm mà ai đến vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's the new model that's \Nalways out of stock!}Đây là mẫu mới nhất luôn hết hàng mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.91,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why is this here?}Tại sao nó lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.37,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is it to your liking?}Chủ nhân có thích không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.49,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The new clothes...}Quần áo mới...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.88,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The pants from this morning...}Quần mình mặc sáng nay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.01,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{And this game console...}Và trò chơi này...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.93,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why is she suddenly giving \Nme all kinds of stuff?!}Tại sao tự nhiên cô ta lại làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.31,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{This is suspicious!}Quá đáng nghi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.99,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What are you trying to \Ndo by giving me things?}Cô cho tôi những thứ này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:26.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{All things I want, too.}Toàn những thứ tôi muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.33,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{As a maid, I...}Tôi là hầu gái...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.23,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're trying to control \Nme by giving me stuff.}Cô muốn kiểm soát tôi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, that's correct.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:41.28,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll tame you and make you mine.}Tôi muốn biến ngài thành của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.92,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What would you do if I said that?}Thì ngài sẽ làm thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.41,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're never going to tame me.}Đừng hòng tôi trở thành của cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.54,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm not going to do as you please!}Tôi sẽ không làm theo ý cô đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:58.88,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't need to be baited with things \Nto know that you're attractive.}Tôi không cần bị mồi để nhận ra sự quyến rũ của cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.05,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Don't underestimate me \Njust because I'm a child!}Đừng xem thường một thằng nhóc!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm going to be the one to make }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{ mine!}Tôi mới là người biến cô thành của mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.52,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{U-Um...}Hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.31,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're going to be mine!}Cô sẽ trở thành của tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.53,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{More, please.}Phần nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.58,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{U-Understood.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:24.29,Show_Title - Sus Maid,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord2\fscx66\fscy66\pos(176,310)}{The }{\fs40\c&H953CA0&}{Maid }{\c\fs}{I Hired Recently\NIs }{\fs40\c&H953CA0&}{Mysterious}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The Maid I Hired Recently Is Mysterious}{\i0}{.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.95,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I've made tea, young master.}Tôi đã pha trà rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:35.63,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:43.52,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I've baked some pastries, young master.}Tôi nướng ít bánh đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.80,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Would you like to try them?}Ngài muốn thử chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.43,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, is there \Nanything you're stuck on?}Chủ nhân, ngài có chỗ nào chưa hiểu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:54.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, shall I sharpen your pencil?}Tôi chuốt bút chì nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, would you like some more tea?}Chủ nhân, ngài có cần thêm trà không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.51,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.70,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Shut up!}Im đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.79,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What's going on with you?!}Cô bị sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:07.40,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What are you trying to accomplish \Nby interfering with my studying?!}Sao cứ làm phiền khi tôi đang học?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{My apologies.}Xin thứ lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:13.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I just want to make myself \Nas useful to you as I can.}Tôi chỉ muốn tỏ ra hữu dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.57,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're going to distract me either way.}Cô đang làm phiền tôi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.30,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You might as well stay \Nnext to me while I study.}Nếu thế thì qua ngồi cạnh tôi lúc đang học.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.67,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That'll keep you from getting lonely, right?}Cô sẽ không cô đơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.12,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It wasn't that I was lonely at all.}Không phải là tôi cô đơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:40.70,sign_9308_61_The_Maid_I_Hired,Text,0,0,0,,{The }{\c&H953CA0&}{Maid }{\c}{I Hired Recently\NIs }{\c&H953CA0&}{Mysterious}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.43,Top Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The Maid I Hired Recently Is Mysterious}{\i0}{.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.57,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, \NLilith has been gone a while.}Cơ mà Lilith không quay lại nữa nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.25,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{My apologies, young master.}Xin thứ lỗi, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.51,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll be leaving for a moment.}Tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.97,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay, got it.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.63,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{All right.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.20,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Way too suspicious!}Quá đáng ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.44,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why is she so restless?}Tại sao cô ta lại vội vã?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.55,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The backyard?}Sân sau?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.77,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What business does she have in the backyard?}Cô ta làm gì ở đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.18,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There must be some kind of secret.}Hẳn là có bí mật.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.04,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Today's the day I find out.}Hôm nay mình sẽ tìm cho ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.27,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She's been playing with a stray cat?}Cô ta chơi với mèo hoang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.06,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Meow.}Nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.88,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I never knew she could make such a face.}Không ngờ cô ta lại có khuôn mặt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Oh, young master.}Chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.79,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Would you like to pet it, too?}Ngài có thích nuôi thú không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:01.25,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This kitty is very calm and friendly.}Con mèo này dễ thương và thân thiện lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No, I'll pass.}Không, tôi không.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.99,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You will?}Vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.75,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Nhưng nó dễ thương lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:16.34,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Could it be that you'd \Nlike \me to pet you, too?}Hay ngài thích được tôi nựng như nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.93,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Of course not!}Vớ vẩn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.77,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm just afraid of cats!}Tôi chỉ sợ mèo thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:20.88,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Besides...}Với cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're even cuter!}Cô dễ thương hơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:30.85,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I couldn't help but admire how beautifully \Npicturesque you were petting the cat.}Tôi bị mê hoặc bởi hình ảnh cô vuốt ve con mèo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:35.00,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But I couldn't come closer \Nbecause I'm afraid of cats!}Nhưng không thể đến gần vì sợ mèo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:40.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What is it so happy about?}Tại sao nó lại vui?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.24,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, that only applies to dogs.}Đây là đặc tính của chó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This cat is indicating that it's angry.}Vừa rồi là tín hiệu nó đang giận.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:50.35,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It seems to have been \Nstartled by your voice.}Có vẻ nó bất ngờ vì giọng của ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.41,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What's the matter, young master?}Sao vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I want to get over my fear of cats.}Tôi muốn vượt qua nỗi sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.85,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.59,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Then I shall help.}Thế thì tôi sẽ giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:10.01,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith, I'm the master of this mansion.}Lilith, tôi là chủ nhân dinh thự này.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.35,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can handle it myself.}Tôi tự làm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.76,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Then I shall be in the mansion.}Vậy tôi sẽ vào nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:21.03,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Please let me know if you need anything.}Nếu cần gì ngài cứ gọi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.49,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's it!}Chính nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.05,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{One more time.}Lần nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master.}Chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith. What is it?}Có chuyện gì Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:12.20,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I kept some of the fish from \Nbreakfast for the cat.}Tôi mang ít cá dư của bữa sáng cho nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm about to leave to go shopping.}Giờ tôi đi mua sắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:18.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Could you please feed it in my place?}Liệu ngài có thể thay tôi cho nó ăn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:19.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Được.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.46,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Leave it to me.}Cứ để tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.43,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you, young master.}Cảm ơn ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.33,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.00,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{D-Do you like it?}M-Mày thích nó hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.43,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I wonder if I can touch it now.}Nếu là giờ thì có thể chạm vào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:02.09,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is it trying to protect me?}Nó đang muốn bảo vệ mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.69,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Th-That was scary.}Đ-Đáng sợ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:37.35,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I hope the young master is all right.}Hi vọng chủ nhân vẫn ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Oh... Young master...}Ồ... chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Look, Lilith!}Nhìn nè Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:49.41,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can touch cats now.}Tôi có thể chạm vào nó rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's an amazing improvement \Nin such a short time.}Chỉ trong thời gian ngắn sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.30,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm the master of this mansion, after all.}Tôi là chủ nhân dinh thự mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.88,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There, there.}Ngoan ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.68,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There, there.}Ngoan ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.77,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Good kitty.}Mèo ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:05.01,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're so soft to the touch.}Mày mềm mại ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're so cute.}Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.29,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, w-would you...}Chủ nhân, tôi cũng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.30,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Would you pet...}Tôi cũng muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.41,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Never mind.}Không có gì ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:22.05,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Good for you, getting petted\Nby the young master.}Mày thật may mắn khi chủ nhân vuốt ve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Y-Young master?}C-Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.83,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You're soft to the touch, too.}Cô cũng mềm mại nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I should make lunch.}Tôi đi làm bữa trưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.85,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll be back inside.}Nên xin phép vào trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.14,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, you dropped something.}Cô đánh rơi gì nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.26,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why do you have a photo of me?!}T-Tại sao lại mang theo ảnh tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:51.05,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You caught me.}Lộ rồi sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:57.68,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's just something I secretly keep with me \Nso I can always see my adorable master.}Chỉ là tôi muốn giữ chủ nhân\N dễ thương bên mình mọi lúc thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:00.49,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why don't you look at the real thing, then?}Vậy thì cứ nhìn người thật đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I won't run or hide.}Tôi không bỏ chạy hay trốn đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.64,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why are you running?}Sao cô lại bỏ chạy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.77,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is this a sneak photo?}Là ảnh chụp trộm nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.64,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wait...}Khoan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.30,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is it for some curse?!}Là lời nguyền gì đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.28,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There's definitely something \Nsuspicious about her.}Chắc chắn có gì đó đáng nghi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:44.54,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, lunch is ready.}Chủ nhân, bữa trưa đã sẵn sàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay. I'll be right there.}Rồi, tôi đến ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.85,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Your morning glory bloomed beautifully.}Hoa bìm bìm của ngài nở đẹp thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.88,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I've been watering it every day.}Ngày nào tôi cũng tưới nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.33,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm not showing you yet.}Chưa được xem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yet?}Chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.88,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's have lunch now.}Thôi, đi ăn nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}C-Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.27,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Let's eat.}Mời dùng bữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:15.01,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Delicious.}Ngon quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.93,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Way too delicious!}Quá ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.98,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There must be some secret.}Có bí mật gì chăng?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.05,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There must be...}Có thể là...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:29.95,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.35,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith, teach me how to cook.}Lilith, dạy tôi nấu ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:37.09,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But I want to make your meals for you.}Nhưng tôi muốn làm bữa ăn cho ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.60,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I want to learn how to cook.}Tôi muốn học nấu ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.92,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{My.}Chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.55,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She distracted me the last time I asked.}Lần trước mình bị làm phân tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.80,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I put a love potion in it.}Tôi đã bỏ tình dược vào đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.76,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But today, I'm going to find out.}Nhưng hôm nay phải tìm cho ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:58.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Could it be that you want me to teach you, \Nhand in hand, step by step?}Ngài muốn tôi cầm tay chỉ dẫn từng bước sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.35,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:06.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Your dishes are better than \Nanything I've ever had.}Khả năng nấu ăn của cô quá tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I want to eat your cooking every day.}Tôi muốn ăn món cô nấu mỗi ngày!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{In fact, I want to marry you.}Không, tôi muốn cưới cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.84,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Marry...}C-Cưới...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:17.29,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So I want to be sure I know \Nhow to cook like you.}Thế nên tôi muốn biết nấu ăn giống cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Shall we make your favorite stew, then?}V-Vậy chúng ta nấu thử món hầm mà ngài thích nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.60,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Stew, huh? Sounds good!}Hầm à? Được đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:35.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Shall we cut the vegetables first?}Vậy thì hãy cắt rau củ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.40,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.90,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, curl your left hand.}Chủ nhân, tay trái phải nắm lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.36,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Hold it like a cat's paw.}Giống như tay mèo đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.29,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Don't tense up. Slowly.}Đừng vội vã, chạm rãi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.66,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{There. That's good.}Phải rồi. Đúng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:57.08,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's like I'm embracing \Nyou right now, isn't it?}Cứ như tôi đang ôm ngài vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.40,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Did you say something?}Cô nói gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.84,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, mind your hand!}Chủ nhân, xin hãy chú ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.05,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's your fault for talking to me.}Tại cô bắt chuyện tôi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.76,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{My apologies.}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.47,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What do I do next?}Tiếp theo làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.13,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Next...}Tiếp theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.58,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's pretty good for my \Nfirst time, isn't it?}Lần đầu mà cũng khá ổn nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Very impressive, young master.}Không hổ danh là ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.01,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Aren't you going to sit down, Lilith?}Cô không ngồi à, Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.08,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{U-Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.47,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you sure I may join you?}Tôi được phép sao ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.26,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah, of course.}Ừm, dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.59,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Let's eat together.}Ăn cùng nhau đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.11,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Then, with your permission...}Vậy thì tôi xin phép...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.78,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Mời dùng bữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:11.09,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She didn't put anything \Nsuspicious in it, though.}Cơ mà cô ta không bỏ gì đáng ngờ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.01,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's delicious, young master.}Ngon quá chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.93,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's okay.}Cũng bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.79,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's very delicious.}Nó rất ngon mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:23.89,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No, it doesn't taste the same as usual.}Không, không như vị mọi khi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.25,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Are you sure it's the same recipe?}Cô chắc là cùng công thức chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:30.59,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It tastes better to me than usual.}Với tôi thì nó ngon hơn mọi khi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:34.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I may have forgotten a secret ingredient.}Có thể tôi quên nguyên liệu bí mật.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.48,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I knew it!}Quả nhiên!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.31,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I always use plenty of it.}Lúc nào tôi cũng bỏ rất nhiều vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:44.31,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The secret ingredient is my \Nlove for my young master.}Đó là tình yêu của tôi dành cho ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.03,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just kiddi—}Đùa--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.02,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I see! It's love!}Ra là thế! Tình yêu à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:53.41,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It makes me happy because you make it \Njust for me, with my happiness in mind.}Nó làm tôi vui vì cô\N nấu cho riêng mình tôi, với tình yêu đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wait...}Không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:59.86,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The reason why the mansion \Nis always so spotless,}Lý do dinh thự luôn sáng bóng,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:04.21,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{and why my torn clothes are \Nsuddenly in perfect shape...}và quần áo phẳng phiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.96,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is it all because you're full of love for me?}là vì cô dành tình yêu cho tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.18,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Amazing!}Tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.07,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{How are you able to have \Nso much love all the time?}Làm sao để cô đong đầy tình yêu vào vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:23.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's a secret for now.}Bí mật...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.38,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{This was a long day.}Hôm nay nhiều chuyện xảy ra ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:39.06,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It was a good day, though.}Nhưng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Hm?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:54.14,sign_26833_232_The_flowers_bloo,Text,0,0,0,,{The flowers bloomed.\NThey're a pretty color, \Nlike Lilith's eyes.}Hoa đã nở\N Chúng thật đẹp\N Có màu như mắt Lilith
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.43,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Hang on...}Khoan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:03.05,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{How did she know I love stew?}Sao cô ta biết mình thích món hầm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You must be exhausted after today.}Hôm nay hẳn ngài đã mệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.52,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Please get plenty of rest tonight.}Xin hãy nghỉ ngơi đi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:19.09,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Well, goodnight, young master.}Chúc ngủ ngon, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.79,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Goodnight.}Ngủ ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:28.41,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{When does Lilith ever sleep?}Lilith khi nào mới ngủ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:35.59,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It seems like she's working before \NI wake up and after I go to sleep.}Ngủ sau mình và dậy trước mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.18,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Suspicious!}Quá đáng nghi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:43.62,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She must be doing something really \Nsuspicious while I'm asleep,}Nhất định cô ta làm gì đó mờ ám trong khi mình ngủ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.18,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{something she can't tell me about.}Chuyện gì đó không thể nói ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.32,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Today's the day I stay up and find out.}Hôm nay mình sẽ điều tra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.12,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.44,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why do you always go to sleep after me?}Sao lúc nào cô cũng ngủ sau tôi?
